### Create Guest State volume and runtime with read-write/read-only Allowed Folders

$ container volume create sand-validation-state
sand-validation-state
[exit 0]

$ container run --name sand-validation-spike --detach --cpus 4 --memory 8G --volume sand-validation-state:/state --mount type=bind,source=/tmp/sand-backend-validation/rw,target=/workspace/rw --mount type=bind,source=/tmp/sand-backend-validation/ro,target=/workspace/ro,readonly sand-validation-dev:latest sleep 10000
